aces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好撚難受好撚痛苦⋯ 時間過得特別慢  好似過左兩三個月咁   但其實一個月都未有⋯<br />\n女人話變就變  話走就走  好撚絕情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好撚想快啲解脫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"1388b0b50751224a7fb549836bc2770598facfad","tid":379843,"uid":5806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T04:49:39.000Z","msg":"唔想咁快醒咪由自己頹下先囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但頹夠就唔該你企返起身繼續行唔好再原地踏步<br />\n去玩下新活動試下新野增值下自己先係最重要<br />\n唔好比自己有停落嚟嘅時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"612a25c60ac5686e9817a72d34d000da801fecbb","tid":379843,"uid":53947,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T05:00:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>分左兩三年 前幾日同返ex閒聊 佢提起有心儀對象而且發展得幾好<br />\n我個心'那'左下。然後祝福佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n初戀真係最難放低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n到底同ex講嘢係咩心態<br />\n同一個曾經同你愛得轟轟烈烈嘅人講嘢<br />\n諗返以為啲事好咩喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbb60677ca0260445d21c98cf366cd121743ff79","tid":379843,"uid":53947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T05:01:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔想咁快醒咪由自己頹下先囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但頹夠就唔該你企返起身繼續行唔好再原地踏步<br />\n去玩下新活動試下新野增值下自己先係最重要<br />\n唔好比自己有停落嚟嘅時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇錯<br />\n頹一排<br />\n痛要痛快"},{"pid":"33f7093e7c0060b5e3eb01a699f4381fa7a31911","tid":379843,"uid":49456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T05:09:28.000Z","msg":"Block.左佢唔好睇<br />\n你會好過啲"},{"pid":"3cdd46ee2bd8c81a618092b18b5c2d573f6b70b9","tid":379843,"uid":73530,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T05:15:42.000Z","msg":"分咗兩個月 就失眠咗兩個月<br />\n其實仲好好好好愛佢<br />\n好掛住佢啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e7bfb438871e14adb0431c57ff2074f2ac0f3b9","tid":379843,"uid":3162,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T05:34:42.000Z","msg":"成日幻想會唔會有一日撞到佢<br />\n因為自從分手之後都無見過<br />\n我會想同佢講下嘢 幾句都好<br />\n明明以前最熟悉最了解 連佢今日有無屙屎都會知 <br />\n呢個一齊左幾年嘅人 原來喺分手嗰刻<br />\n已經代表左我同佢生死不相往來<br />\n唔會再知道 你過成點了 <br />\n但個心 仍然有替你打氣架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"185df3b02956339265281fad9915daa6ec367294","tid":379843,"uid":84646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T05:37:57.000Z","msg":"初戀分手咗已經三年...間唔中仲會諗起佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86c5a29977df4a143cddfde95382c95f6515777b","tid":379843,"uid":129187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T07:17:10.000Z","msg":"擔心佢過得好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bb1b4fa07d692de571c9b1b7bb090233dc66c06","tid":379843,"uid":88213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T10:02:08.000Z","msg":"好想知佢每日發生乜事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但已經無資格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" 